summary: An Ordinance authorizing the dismissal of a suit to condemn private property for the laying off, extending and establishing of West Fifty-ninth Street et al. As provided for in Ordinance 31915, Cause No. 100903, insofar as the same affects certain property in Tracts Nineteen (190, Twenty-two (22), Twenty-three (230, Twenty-four (24), Twenty-nine (29), Thirty (30), Thirty-one (31) and Thirty-two (32), Ballard Acre Tracts, an addition to the City of Seattle.
